  "local_port": 35578,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "How do I increase font size in Quora?",
  "response": "Quora does not currently offer a built-in feature to change the font size directly within the platform. However, you can increase the font size by using browser settings or extensions. Here are a few methods you can try:\n\n### 1. **Using Browser Zoom:**\nMost web browsers allow you to zoom in and out, which effectively changes the font size of the content displayed.\n\n- **Google Chrome:** \n  - Click the three vertical dots in the upper-right corner.\n  - Use the \"+\" button to zoom in.\n\n- **Firefox:** \n  - Click the three horizontal lines in the upper-right corner.\n  - Use the \"+\" button to zoom in.\n\n- **Safari:** \n  - Click \"View\" in the menu bar.\n  - Select \"Zoom In.\"\n\n### 2. **Custom CSS:**\nIf you're comfortable with using browser extensions, you can add custom CSS to change the font size.\n\n- **Stylus Extension (Chrome/Firefox):**\n  - Install the Stylus extension.\n  - Create a new style for Quora.\n  - Add custom CSS like:\n    ```css\n    body {\n        font-size: 18px; /* Change this value to your preferred font size */\n    }\n    ```\n  - Save and apply the style.\n\n### 3. **Accessibility Settings:**\nMany operating systems have built-in accessibility features that allow you to increase the text size across all applications.\n\n- **Windows:**\n  - Go to Settings > Ease of Access > Display.\n  - Adjust the \"Make text bigger\" slider.\n\n- **MacOS:**\n  - Go to System Preferences > Accessibility > Display.\n  - Adjust the \"Text size\" slider.\n\n### 4. **Reader Mode:**\nSome browsers have a Reader Mode that simplifies the page layout and often allows you to adjust text size.\n\n- **Safari:**\n  - Click the Reader button in the URL bar (looks like a page icon).\n  - Adjust the text size using the \"Aa\" button.\n\n- **Firefox:**\n  - Click the Reader View button in the URL bar (looks like an open book).\n  - Adjust the text size using the \"Aa\" button.\n\nBy using one or more of these methods, you should be able to increase the font size on Quora to make reading more comfortable for you.",
